        }, 
        {
            "date": "2009-09-30 11:04:20", 
            "sentences": [
                {
                    "is_in_lex_summary": true, 
                    "text": "\"keyworded url functionality has nothing to do with setting your default search \nengine.\"", 
                    "is_in_email_summary": false
                }, 
                {
                    "is_in_lex_summary": false, 
                    "text": "", 
                    "is_in_email_summary": false
                }, 
                {
                    "is_in_lex_summary": false, 
                    "text": "No, it doesn't.", 
                    "is_in_email_summary": false
                }, 
                {
                    "is_in_lex_summary": true, 
                    "text": "And managing search engines covers far more than just setting a \ndefault engine.", 
                    "is_in_email_summary": false
                }, 
                {
                    "is_in_lex_summary": true, 
                    "text": "That's why there's a management UI at all, not just a \"pick a \ndefault\" dropdown in the options.", 
                    "is_in_email_summary": false
                }, 
                {
                    "is_in_lex_summary": false, 
                    "text": "", 
                    "is_in_email_summary": false
                }, 
                {
                    "is_in_lex_summary": true, 
                    "text": "\"i suggest you break off from the firefox setup\"", 
                    "is_in_email_summary": false
                }, 
                {
                    "is_in_lex_summary": false, 
                    "text": "", 
                    "is_in_email_summary": false
                }, 
                {
                    "is_in_lex_summary": false, 
                    "text": "We did.", 
                    "is_in_email_summary": false
                }, 
                {
                    "is_in_lex_summary": true, 
                    "text": "That's precisely why we have a set of search engines with optional keywords, \nwhich covers this case far better than conflating them with bookmarks ever did.", 
                    "is_in_email_summary": false
                }, 
                {
                    "is_in_lex_summary": false, 
                    "text": "", 
                    "is_in_email_summary": false
                }, 
                {
                    "is_in_lex_summary": true, 
                    "text": "\"since the bookmarks section is probably where you will continue to store these url \nsettings\"", 
                    "is_in_email_summary": false
                }, 
                {
                    "is_in_lex_summary": false, 
                    "text": "", 
                    "is_in_email_summary": false
                }, 
                {
                    "is_in_lex_summary": true, 
                    "text": "We have never stored search engines in the bookmarks storage system.", 
                    "is_in_email_summary": false
                }, 
                {
                    "is_in_lex_summary": false, 
                    "text": "", 
                    "is_in_email_summary": false
                }, 
                {
                    "is_in_lex_summary": true, 
                    "text": "\"might also have the effect of highlighting its existence to people who do look \naround at their options\"", 
                    "is_in_email_summary": false
                }, 
                {
                    "is_in_lex_summary": false, 
                    "text": "", 
                    "is_in_email_summary": false
                }, 
                {
                    "is_in_lex_summary": false, 
                    "text": "Non-goal, plus this fraction of users is extremely low.", 
                    "is_in_email_summary": false
                }, 
                {
                    "is_in_lex_summary": true, 
                    "text": "In fact, we would probably \nprefer that people not play around with or know about this stuff, as it tends to be \npretty confusing.", 
                    "is_in_email_summary": false
                }, 
                {
                    "is_in_lex_summary": false, 
                    "text": "", 
                    "is_in_email_summary": false
                }, 
                {
                    "is_in_lex_summary": true, 
                    "text": "We do intend to add a context menu \"Add a keyword for this search\" option when right-\nclicking search fields in web content.", 
                    "is_in_email_summary": false
